    <abstract>
      <t>It is in the interest of the Mobile IP WG to conserve the usage of the type field since we see many drafts proposing new extensions for Mobile IP. Therefore there is a real need to find ways to limit the usage of the type field in the extensions structure. MIER describes a new extension structure to Mobile IP to make the extensions far more extensible.</t>
